pha-sapphire", "text": "The base of volcanoes is where they make their homes. They shoot fire from their five horns to repel attacking enemies."}, {"version": "black", "text": "This Pok\u00e9mon was believed to have been born from the sun. When it evolves, its entire body is engulfed in flames."}, {"version": "black-2", "text": "Said to have been born from the sun, it spews fire from its horns and encases itself in a cocoon of fire when it evolves."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "Said to have been born from the sun, it spews fire from its horns and encases itself in a cocoon of fire when it evolves."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "Larvesta\u2019s body is warm all over. It spouts fire from the tips of its horns to intimidate predators and scare prey."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "The people of ancient times believed that Larvesta fell from the sun."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "It protects itself with flame. Long years ago, people believed Larvesta had a nest on the sun."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "When battling opponents, it sprays fire from its five horns. The max temperature of the flames can reach nearly 5,500 degrees Fahrenheit."}, {"version": "white", "text": "The base of volcanoes is where they make their homes. They shoot fire from their five horns to repel attacking enemies."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "Said to have been born from the sun, it spews fire from its horns and encases itself in a cocoon of fire when it evolves."}, {"version": "x", "text": "Said to have been born from the sun, it spews fire from its horns and encases itself in a cocoon of fire when it evolves."}, {"version": "y", "text": "The base of volcanoes is where they make their homes. They shoot fire from their five horns to repel attacking enemies."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "om